<P>Cele&s;tina entered trembling; and fearing
the &s;ight of Vava&s;our, whom &s;he had never
met &s;ince the terrifying night at Ranelagh;
but the moment &s;he beheld Emily, &s;he no
longer thought of any thing but the affecting
