<P>Lady Horatia then ha&s;tened to the chamber
of Cele&s;tina; &s;he was ju&s;t in bed&mdash;but knowing
who it was tapped at the door, begged her to
Come in:&mdash;</P>
<P>"Well, my dear child," &s;aid Lady Horatia,
"and what is all this? I am impatient to
